Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reset_path_adjust_group(25.10)                  reset_path_adjust_group(25.10)

Name
       reset_path_adjust_group  -  Removes all path adjust groups that are set
       using the set_path_adjust command for  setting  path  slack  adjustment
       values

Syntax
       reset_path_adjust_group

       [-help]

       [-name <group_name> | -all]

       Removes  all  path adjust groups that are set using the set_path_adjust
       command for setting path slack adjustment values.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       -all   Removes all the path adjust groups.

       -name <group_name>
              Removes the named path adjust group completely.

Related Information
              * set_path_adjust_group

              * set_path_adjust

